body_html:
I ran a build with

cmake .. -A x64 -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ^
-DSWIG_EXECUTABLE=C:/swigwin-3.0.12/swig.exe ^
-DPYTHON_EXECUTABLE=C:/Users/tknight/AppData/Local/Programs/Python/Python35/python.exe ^
-DPYTHON_LIBRARIES=C:/Users/tknight/AppData/Local/Programs/Python/Python35/libs/python35.lib ^
-Dtensorflow_WIN_CPU_SIMD_OPTIONS=/arch:AVX

MSBuild /p:Configuration=Release tf_python_build_pip_package.vcxproj /fl1 /fl2 /fl3 /flp2:logfile=JustErrors.log;errorsonly /flp3:logfile=JustWarnings.log;warningsonly

and it built ok (no errors), so the problem appears to be limited to the combination of tensorflow with GPU and arch:AVX.
